## Technological Support: Connect Care Clinical Information System

The Connect Care CIS exemplifies how technology supports interprofessional collaboration by:

- Providing navigators and order sets tailored to phases of care.
- Enabling medication, problem, and order reconciliation during interfacility transfers.
- Facilitating electronic documentation accessible to sending and receiving teams.
- Supporting RAAPID consultations and repatriation orders to streamline transfers.
- Allowing for leave of absence and direct admission workflows within the system.

This comprehensive system reduces information gaps and coordinates care across teams and facilities ([Alberta Health Services, 2024](https://www.albertahealthservices.ca/assets/info/hp/cc/if-cc-manual-patient-movement.pdf)).

